<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_368" id="183v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_368_r2l1">Graf <expan>Ludwıge<ex>n</ex></expan> von Ötingen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_368_r2l2">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der ~ Stromerin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r2l3"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin wegen / dauon <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir mit Jr geredt vnd die ſpricht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r2l5">Sıe vvölle <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden ſelber ein <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_368_r2l4">darumb </ab></add> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd wo etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_368" id="183v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Graf <expan>Ludwige<ex>n</ex></expan> von Ötingen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gnade <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der Stromerin,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin, wegen, davon
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir mit ir geredt und die spricht, sie
                        wölle <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden selber ein
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<add>darumb</add>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wo etc.</ab>
</div>
